The paper deals with capacity analysis of noncoherent fading relay channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the accuracy of predicting fading coefficients, which is a problem in networked systems (cs.NI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also deals with communication rates and capacity of channels, which are topics in communication theory (cs.COMM). Finally, the paper mentions multiple-input single-output fading channels, which is a topic in multimedia systems (cs.MM).
